    public abstract class HttpRestR66ClientResponseHandler
extends org.jboss.netty.channel.SimpleChannelUpstreamHandler
    Rest client response handler. Note: by default, no connection are closed except in case of error or if in HTTP 1.0 or explicitly to be closed.
